"The untold story, the process, the hustle. 🎥 #BehindTheScenes"

NEVER EVER  EVER...

Buy shoes which feel uncomfortable in the first 30 seconds of wearing them. The sales people may push you to buy cause they want to make a sale... Typical reasons - the shoes will expand, after a few times of wearing them, they will take shape of your feet. These are reasons which are never good enough, and you may end up never wearing the shoes even once as they feel uncomfortable in the first place. 

Sometimes even people you are shopping with may push you to buy cause they are tired, bored or just want you to make a decision.

Trust your instincts, trust the feeling when you put on the shoes, your body will give you enough signs if the shoes are worth buying or not.

Remember a wrong pair of shoe will show very clearly in your walk, on your face and could absolutely even ruin your day! 

Choose wisely and invest time in finding the right fit.
